(49026, 3, 0, 'I''ll not hear a word of it. The egg is yours. I want you to see how committed I am to this union.', 12, 0, 100, 25, 0, 0, 0, 'Kurdran Wildhammer to Player'),
(49026, 4, 0, 'And how committed the Alliance is to the Wildhammer cause!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 'Kurdran Wildhammer to Player'),
(49026, 5, 0, 'Ah, look. Here comes $n, escorting your bride!', 12, 0, 100, 25, 0, 0, 0, 'Kurdran Wildhammer to Player'),
(49027, 0, 0, 'I hope you''re right, Kurdran old friend.', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 'Keegan Firebeard to Player'),
(49027, 1, 0, 'Kurdran - no, I couldn''t! Sky''ree was a legend, I can''t-', 12, 0, 100, 274, 0, 0, 0, 'Keegan Firebeard to Player'),
(49027, 2, 0, 'Aye. Thank you, Kurdran.', 12, 0, 100, 2, 0, 0, 0, 'Keegan Firebeard to Player'),
(49027, 3, 0, 'I do.', 12, 0, 100, 273, 0, 0, 0, 'Keegan Firebeard to Grundy MacGraff'),
(49028, 0, 0, 'Where''s your "honor" now, Horde scum?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Tidebreaker Sailor to Axebite Infantry'),
(49034, 0, 0, 'Ladies and gentledwarves, we gather here in the shadow of Thunderstrike to honor the union of Fanny Thundermar and Keegan Firebeard.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Grundy MacGraff to Player'),
(49034, 1, 0, 'May their bond be as eternal as the wind, waves, stone and fire. ', 12, 0, 100, 274, 0, 0, 0, 'Grundy MacGraff to Player'),
(49034, 2, 0, 'Do you, Keegan and Fanny, accept one another into your lives, that two become as one, in union everlasting?', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 'Grundy MacGraff to Player'),
(49034, 3, 0, 'Then, by the powers vested in me... the powers vested in me...', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'Grundy MacGraff to Player'),
(49034, 4, 0, '...BY BLOOD AND SHADOW!', 12, 0, 100, 15, 0, 0, 0, 'Grundy MacGraff to Player'),
(49034, 5, 0, 'I shall consume your lifeblood in the name of the master!!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 'Grundy MacGraff to Player'),
(49163, 0, 0, 'SAVE THE WEDDING!', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Kirthaven Wedding Vehicle to Player'),
(49212, 0, 0, 'The bombs are set! Run to the balcony and jump to escape!', 42, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Skyshredder Bomb Controller Bunny to Player'),
(49212, 1, 0, 'BOOM!', 42, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Skyshredder Bomb Controller Bunny to Player'),
(49234, 0, 0, '|TInterface\\Icons\\spell_holy_prayerofshadowprotection.blp:20|t The Beast Unleashed begins to emit an |cFFFF0000|Hspell:93717|h[Aura of Darkness]|h|r!', 41, 0, 100, 53, 0, 14046, 0, 'The Beast Unleashed'),
(49234, 1, 0, 'Uulwi gag erh''ongg w''ssh.', 14, 0, 100, 53, 0, 14046, 0, 'The Beast Unleashed'),
(49252, 0, 0, 'Oh, like you coulda done any better.', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 'Fargo Flintlocke to Player'),
(49275, 0, 0, 'Get it! Kill it!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 14046, 0, 'Keely Dunwald'),
(49277, 0, 0, 'It''s one of them!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14046, 0, 'Iain Firebeard'),
(49278, 0, 0, 'Stop that thing!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14046, 0, 'Cliff Thundermar'),
(49279, 0, 0, 'For the Wildhammer!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14046, 0, 'Russell Brower to The Beast Unleashed'),
(49314, 0, 0, 'Waaaaahhhhh!!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14046, 0, 'Donnelly Dunwald'),
(49361, 0, 0, 'You''re okay, Firebeard. *urp* You''re okay by me.', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 'Colin Thundermar'),
(49363, 0, 0, 'Twilight''s Hammer don''t scare me none. Bring ''em on!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 'Keely Dunwald'),
(49364, 0, 0, 'BEST! WEDDING! EVAR! *Hic*', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 'Eoin Dunwald'),
(49548, 0, 0, 'Kazum ', 14, 1, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 'Krazzworks Laborer'),
(49548, 1, 0, 'Moth''aga gesh ', 14, 1, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 'Krazzworks Laborer'),
(49548, 2, 0, 'L regAs grom ', 14, 1, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Krazzworks Laborer'),
(49548, 3, 0, 'Ha thok GUl gesh''zugas il gesh ha osh''kava magan tov''nokaz zaga nogu thok ', 14, 1, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 'Krazzworks Laborer'),
(49548, 4, 0, 'MOg no''ku re''ka Gesh ', 14, 1, 100, 274, 0, 0, 0, 'Krazzworks Laborer'),
(49548, 5, 0, 'Kaz ogg Gesh ', 14, 1, 100, 274, 0, 0, 0, 'Krazzworks Laborer'),
(49548, 6, 0, 'L re''Ka ogar il kil ', 14, 1, 100, 274, 0, 0, 0, 'Krazzworks Laborer'),
(49818, 0, 0, 'Neltharion! Look at yourself. Misshapen. Twisted. You''re coming apart.', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 21049, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Player'),
(49820, 0, 0, 'Just as all life ends in death ... all order must end in chaos ... Come! Embrace the inevitable, as I have!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 20278, 0, 'Deathwing to Player'),
(49820, 1, 0, 'The sun has set on this mortal world, fools. Make peace with your end, for the hour of Twilight falls.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Deathwing to Deathwing and Alexstrasza Fight Vehicle - Cutscene [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(50286, 0, 0, 'Yep! Off we go.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Fargo Flintlocke to Flintlocke''s Seaplane'),
(50286, 1, 0, 'Easy ... does it...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Fargo Flintlocke to Flintlocke''s Seaplane'),
(50286, 2, 0, 'Right then. I hate long plane rides. So I''mma gonna kick in the after-market burners and ignite our entire fuel supply in one go.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Fargo Flintlocke to Flintlocke''s Seaplane'),
(50286, 3, 0, 'Whatever yeh do... Don''t. Black. Out!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Fargo Flintlocke to Flintlocke''s Seaplane'),
(50360, 0, 0, 'Flintlocke, if we have a big giant cannon, why don''t we just shoot ... a cannonball?', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, '"Doc" Schweitzer'),
(50465, 0, 0, 'Good work. I''ll keep the men pushing from here. Move forward and take the last gate.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Master Mathias Shaw to Player'),
(50469, 0, 0, 'Here we go. Hold on tight!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Stormcaller Mylra to Earthen Ring Gryphon'),
(50469, 1, 0, 'Watch those tentacles! Their reach is frightening.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Stormcaller Mylra to Earthen Ring Gryphon'),
(50641, 0, 0, 'Attention!', 14, 7, 100, 15, 0, 0, 0, 'Victor''s Point Captain'),
(51140, 0, 0, 'Don''t let them out of sight! Quickly - come with me!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 21513, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51140, 1, 0, 'The battle is about to begin!', 42, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51140, 2, 0, '|TInterface\\Icons\\spell_fire_flamebolt.blp:32|t  Use Your Fire Blast to incinerate Twilight Shadowdrakes.', 42, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51140, 3, 0, '|TInterface\\Icons\\ability_druid_ravage.blp:32|t  When your enemies are weak, tear them from the sky with your Finishing Strike!', 42, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51140, 4, 0, '|TInterface\\Icons\\spell_nature_healingway.blp:32|t  Your Lifebinder Boon will heal others while restoring your health and mana.', 42, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51159, 0, 0, 'There - they''ve fallen!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 21514, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51159, 1, 0, 'Mother, stay still. Your wounds are great.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 21515, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51159, 2, 0, 'Deathwing - he lives!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51159, 3, 0, 'Mortal, take the dragon queen. Carry her to safety. Now! RUN! Get her away from here!', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 21520, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51159, 4, 0, 'I will delay the Aspect of Death. Take her to safety. GO!', 12, 0, 100, 25, 0, 21521, 0, 'Calen to Player'),
(51171, 0, 0, 'Calen, no!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Calen'),
(51186, 0, 0, 'The black aspect''s blood is cursed. Wherever it was shed - nothing will grow for ten thousand years.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 21050, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Calen'),
(51186, 1, 0, 'The Earth Warder... he is dead.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 21050, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Calen'),
(51186, 2, 0, 'But it is over. We can work now to bottle up the horrors he has unleashed.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 21051, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Calen'),
(51186, 3, 0, 'Impossible!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Calen'),
(51354, 0, 0, 'Mortal, I want you to bear witness to this, but for your own safety stay back. Calen, you too.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 21045, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51354, 1, 0, 'Your life isn''t yours to throw away, Calen. Should I fail, the fate of this world may rest on your shoulders.', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 21046, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51354, 2, 0, 'It pains me, Neltharion - but I must end you, as I have ended Malygos.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 21047, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51354, 3, 0, 'I see the hollow metal shell of a once great ally, and the precious gift of the Titans wasted.', 12, 0, 100, 274, 0, 21048, 0, 'Alexstrasza the Life-Binder to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51355, 0, 0, 'Lifebinder! Do you presume that I am at your beck and call? I have a world to unmake.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 20275, 0, 'Deathwing to Player'),
(51355, 1, 0, '"End" me? Lifebinder, you think life is yours to take away?', 12, 0, 100, 11, 0, 20276, 0, 'Deathwing to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51355, 2, 0, 'Life is weak, mortal, fleeting ... fragile.', 12, 0, 100, 274, 0, 0, 0, 'Deathwing to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51355, 3, 0, 'Death is final. Death is eternal. Death is ... my realm.', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 0, 0, 'Deathwing to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51355, 4, 0, 'Look upon me and you see death incarnate, the unmaker of worlds.', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 0, 'Deathwing to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51355, 5, 0, 'Then witness my new gifts, bestowed by this world''s true masters.', 12, 0, 100, 5, 0, 20277, 0, 'Deathwing to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51356, 0, 0, 'I will not leave your side.', 12, 0, 100, 274, 0, 21510, 0, 'Calen to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51356, 1, 0, 'Yes, mother.', 12, 0, 100, 2, 0, 21512, 0, 'Calen to Deathwing Intro Cutscene Vehicle [INTERNAL ONLY]'),
(51493, 0, 0, 'This changes nothing. (Nothing nothing changes. Crush them, crush.)', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 22102, 0, 'Cho''gall to Player'),
(51493, 1, 0, 'What of our agents in Stormwind? (Stormwind! The eye, the eye sees into the city heart.) Bring me the eye.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 22103, 0, 'Cho''gall to Player'),
(51493, 2, 0, '(Blaspheme! Blaspheme disgust hate hate...) No matter. Where one eye closes, another opens. (The Master sees all! The Master knows all!) We will know our enemy''s hearts, for they are weak. The eye. Now.', 12, 0, 100, 36, 0, 22105, 0, 'Cho''gall to Player'),
(51493, 3, 0, 'The shadow of the Master covers this world... (Darkness, all darkness.) Our enemies fight one another, across the Highland. Fools. (Blood, blood.) WAIT! There is another!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 22106, 0, 'Cho''gall to Eye of Twilight Vehicle');
